reviewText: Works great an shipped on time

I Saw ThisCD At Best Buy Last Year. So I Bough The CD And I Had To Get The DVD. The Songs On The DVD are Longer Then On The CD.I Play This DVD When I Am Down And This DVD Picks Me Up. In This DVD You Will Feel The Power Of God In A Mighty Way And You Will Also Feel That There Is Nothing to Hard For God To Do. I Also Got A Copy For My Best Friend Mother Who Can Not Go To Church So She Can Feel Like She Is at Church. So If You Want To Feel The Power Of God Or If You Need Your Faith In God To Be Made Strong This Is The DVD To Buy. Also The CD Of The Same Name Is Good Too.
